Subject: Whatsapp Upload is Blocking
Description: Hi Team we have not applied any policy block the WhatsApp upload, but for many users whatsapp upload is getting blocked. If I uninstall the EPP then it will start working. Please check on priority.
Solution_Comment__c: We found that the customer had another tool installed which was interfering with ours (Netskope One Client -  a SASE client), when we disabled it EPP resumed to work as expected.  This case I will close now as it is solved.
